Although life can get heavy at times .. I look back and see all the things I wanted / worked for and have now.. Its a big blessing the way time, gods grace, work and persistence bring you to places you dream of. I’m in a season of tremendous change and transition. This year has been a lot. Bought my first house on my own; it’s a fixer investment property. Met the man of my dreams. Decided to transition my business and tons of other changes. In the thick of it your mind can wander into what’s ifs and fear and sometimes that gets tough. But always in aerial view you see how beautiful life is and see how those feelings and moments are just part of the process. EXTRA GRATEFUL AND EXCITED FOR ANOTHER BEAUTIFUL YEAR😙
Only 2 weeks left of 2023.. can you believe it?! 😫
